I don't know about you but 
sometimes I am scared of what I really want. I mean, I know what I want to have and achieve and also my motives behind it but the road to getting there seems so overwhelming sometimes and well just plain scary!
The truth is, sometimes the more scared you are to do something the more it means that's exactly what you are supposed to be doing. All the big turning points in my life over the past few years have been scary. The thing that scares me the most I know is what I truly want and sometimes the fear keeps me stuck but the more I acknowledge it the more I can ask to have deeper faith. Faith and fear cannot exist together. Faith is said to be almost being certain of what we do not see. Its an absolute belief that a higher force is constantly working behind the scenes in every area of our lives, even if there is no tangible evidence to support that fact. On the other hand, fear, simply stated, is unbelief, weak belief or lack of faith. So whenever you feel fear acknowledge it and move through fear into faith. If fear gains the upper hand in our thoughts, it can takes hold of our emotions. Faith in ourselves and the ultimate faith in a higher power can help you move through fear. So be careful what you feed the choice is yours feed your faith or your fears. 
#Faith #Fear #Hope #Love #Desire #TheFoodRemedy #FeedYourMind

I have been able to take 15 vacations since Aug 2015...on top of my few hundred a month, I have paid off an additional 5k in student loans, i have been able to let my wife be a stay at home mom....im not saying this to boast, in fact just the opposite.. I'm not Special. If i can do this you can do this! I didn't graduate college...if I can do this you can do this! I am the  father of 2, husband to 1 if I can do this you can do this. I am a full time employee...if I can do this you can do this. I had every excuse available, no time, too busy, got kids, can't afford it, don't know how, I never done this before, I don't think it's for me! The only thing that has allowed me to have the #Results I have had is simple, I didn't take those excuses, instead I paid attention to people worth paying attention to. People who could afford the lifestyle I wanted for me and my family.. I know #SuccessLeaveClues. I saw an #opportunity instead of an #obstacle. I had #fear, but I have #faith which gave me #courage to act on what I saw...i made a #decision which led me to a #commitment to continue my #actions regardless of naysayers, regardless of rejection, regardless of my circumstances. ..#Regardless! Now all I want to do is help people like YOU do the same thing... because I believe you can do it too! Only question... are you ready to get started or will you let doubt, fear, and excuses hold you back? #TheHustleWillMakeTheDreamTheReality #TeamThrottle #LetsGetIt #JoinTheMovement

Where do I begin?  I feel SO overwhelmed!  I begin right here, right now, IN the present moment, WITH the present moment.  There will be additions and deletions, failures and successes.  I just need to start where I am and move.  My story is unfolding one by one.  One experience, one exploration.  One thought, one word. One paragraph, one post.  I remind myself to be patient with the process.  All will fall into place. . . and most likely not as I forecast.
.
The empowerment comes from moving.
.
Sometimes I do not know where to begin.  Sometimes I do not know where to move.  I know if I stay where I am today, tomorrow I will still be there.  I want to create my life.  Move step by step.  The journey will be imperfect. Perfectly imperfect!  Perfectly imperfect!!
.
